Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得找到基拉·汀斯利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要么跟血腥约翰是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么马上就要成为他下一个目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁干的  告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  她说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说血腥约翰左肩膀有个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的筹码
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:30.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}马里布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,400)\fs18\pos(193.8,204.8)}加利福尼亚  马里布  简的住宅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-简  -喂  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  别这么做  别扔下我这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  求你了  你身处险境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样做是在自寻死路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(189,132)}两天前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,132)\fad(0,400)}星期二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纹身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以用那个来确定血腥约翰的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  -太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们只要一个个检查疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看哪个人身上就纹身就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰还不知道我发现纹身的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果我们去查他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能血腥约翰会发现此事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在我们还没机会接近他的时候就销声匿迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把五名疑犯同时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合到一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再检查是否有纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何才能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就直接叫他们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他们会同意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没打算给他们选择的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成行了  还有个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布莱特·斯特尔斯因两起谋杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被联调局通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  二十多年前的悬案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都过去那么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局现在才跟进吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定是有了什么新的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-法医证据  目击证人  -那斯特尔斯在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键就是这个  没人知道他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连联调局也不知道  斯特尔斯几周前就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  但我们会找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我配合你的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你揭露血腥约翰身份的时候我要在场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我说了好的  -说是说了  但你说的肯定不算数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事没有商量的余地  简
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我百分百同意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为我之前说得够清楚了  探员们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不知道布莱特·斯特尔斯在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们也表达得很清楚了  你这说法我们不买账
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯把天眼组织的领导权留给了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他却没有告诉你他躲藏在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本说不通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯自始至终
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都将教徒的需要放在他自己之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想让我知道是因为他想保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也因为他不想被人找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不觉得布莱特·斯特尔斯担心是否会被找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来很有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯在我们这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实世界里的时间  是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我们说话的这会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在做好心理和身体上的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以摆脱我们这个物质世界的束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是非常天真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常无知的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布莱特·斯特尔斯不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是要将自己提升到一个新的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这种道行不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要非常艰难才能触碰到这种高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然我们中有人对此是无法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡  加了一份奶油  一份糖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了  拉塞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要准备好了的话鉴证小组就要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我查明他的身份  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我怕高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  有人来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰的案子有了重大突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到了一些新线索
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常重要的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  现在还不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道能信任谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道能不能信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰有一些位高权重的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  但不能在这说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八点见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要时间找一个安全的见面地点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  在哪见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到了那天再告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太扯淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经犯过很多次错误了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是低估了血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再犯这种错误了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想知道线索  就要听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是麦卡利斯特警长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警长吗  我是派翠克·简
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克  最近怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我打电话是有事想问你  -问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上个月我去纳帕谷的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说听任我的调遣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说话算数吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我是讲信用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我能指望你帮我个忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八点我需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到那天我再告诉你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于血腥约翰的事  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们准备好了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  伊夫林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这是给您的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}派翠克·简正在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚你们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将见证我升天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这个世界  飞升到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个世外的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要为我哀悼  我的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这并非逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是启程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,131)\fad(0,400)}星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  唐  你养的不是一个情妇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是一个想要报复你  会毁掉你的疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该庆幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的工作就是解决问题  你现在要做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要给她开张支票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给她很大一笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后祈祷这事就这么完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还没完  也别担心  唐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多种办法可以让一个女人闭嘴  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高兴见到你  特蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  请给我来一杯黑咖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上八点把我叫来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个调查需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么  如果你找我帮忙那这就很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  特蕾莎  我还不了解你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和简对血腥约翰的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有进展了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"也许"  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要搞得这么神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的  为什么要瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们该不会觉得我是血腥约翰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就是这么想的  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要想找我问话  那就逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则就别把我扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果问不管用  我不问了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不为加调局工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在无法得到执法人员所能得到的保护了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么  你威胁我  -不是我  是简
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他明天晚上想见你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果不去  他就会认为你是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他会找你麻烦的  雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解简的  你知道他身上发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道血腥约翰对他做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我  我不会拿这个试探他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不怕派翠克·简
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去和他见一面又有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果去了  你和简
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会再怀疑我是血腥约翰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后绝对不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没说完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯特尔斯  -他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他在哪儿  -我帮不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都为天眼组织工作这么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想抓他  我只想跟他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我这个忙  算我欠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早你会需要我帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷·哈弗内说斯特尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一架私人飞机供其往来国内不被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机主是一个名叫莱恩·帕克斯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克斯  知道了  我去查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简到局里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(189.6,266.4)}加州  帕罗奥多  帕罗奥多机场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉莫特先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  有什么可效劳的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周探员  瑞斯比探员  加调局的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想请你回答几个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚有一架G6私人飞机降落在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注册尾号为M550MT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约十一点左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道飞机上的人是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  私人飞机不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提供乘客名单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有碰巧见到有谁从飞机上下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  有汽车服务公司的人来接他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可能帮得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会正好知道那个汽车服务公司的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汽车服务公司那边怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说昨晚从机场接到了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操着英国口音的银发男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯特尔斯  -我们也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地址是厄瓜多尔领事馆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旧金山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的  你们俩去查查看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  范佩尔  不如你一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们能利用这个优势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没有  -没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我没问题的  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-职责所在  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就干点跑腿的活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了  有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈弗内答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  斯特尔斯那边怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩尔好像瞄准他的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她正在查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就还剩一个血腥约翰案疑犯要约谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  伯特仑  我正往他办公室走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-咱们那边见吗  -好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(190.8,267.2)}加利福尼亚  旧金山  厄瓜多尔领事馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾斯·范佩尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次见到你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次有何贵干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是简
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要你帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差你来  他可真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我到底能为派翠克·简做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想见见你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天晚上八点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我们上次一别  你变样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟我说你嫁给那个只会傻笑的呆子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你会去见简吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能见他我再高兴不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很乐意  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不幸的是  鉴于我现在的境况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不太能成行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说因为联邦调查局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你功课做得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不知道我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们也就不知道你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要是不肯见简  他们就会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的确变了  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去过厄瓜多尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很多很多年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那传教来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的人很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有个年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很穷  但野心勃勃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在他身上看到了些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定试着帮帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮他付学费
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也没什么  但你猜怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子已经是国务部长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很为他高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他邀请我住在这豪华的领事馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这一片小小的外国领土上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外国领土  如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不受你们加调局  联调局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与任何美国法律管辖的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  格蕾斯  你的威胁不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  很高兴能再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我跟简问个好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去的时候随手关门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啊  我感觉轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  案子有突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么案子  -血腥约翰案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上就能确定凶手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的确定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你们有了切实答案要立刻告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此案结束的时候我要在场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等您这句话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚和派翠克·简谈了点有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特仑那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了  斯特尔斯那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不太好  -你找到他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住在厄瓜多尔领事馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他在里面  我们就动不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来对付斯特尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会也不必跟你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:21:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我的说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霰弹枪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火力够大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于明天晚上的事  我们得谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经告诉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先听我说完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望我在场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望我在场是因为你觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会阻止你杀血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是你不会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像血腥约翰这种禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本连上庭受审的资格都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种人就该就地正法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  让我搞搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在执法部门干了快二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然就这么改变原则了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:22:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在血腥约翰案上吗  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很惊讶  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你不相信我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我认识的最诚实的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情上  你绝不会骗我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明晚见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明晚见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,131)\fad(0,400)}星期四
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  我亲爱的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近来还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:23:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  那么说你不是来找我聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明晚八点你要来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-派翠克  -不  你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.34,0:24:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你明晚八点来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.93,0:24:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则等到我再回来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这是领事馆也保不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.17,0:24:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的话句句当真
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.39,0:24:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.73,0:24:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.04,0:24:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将死之人还怕什么死亡威胁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.05,0:24:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装模作样骗骗你那些信徒还行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.86,0:24:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗我就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太高估我了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.23,0:24:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常不幸的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.49,0:24:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不是装的了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.71,0:24:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还剩多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.32,0:24:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经扩散到血液了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.67,0:24:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无药可医了  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.24,0:24:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许两周  也许一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.78,0:24:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.29,0:25:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是针对你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.37,0:25:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间对我来说太宝贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.94,0:25:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我还是需要你来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.43,0:25:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.45,0:25:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事如此重要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.89,0:25:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.55,0:25:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于接近他了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.28,0:25:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前所未有的接近
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.58,0:25:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.84,0:25:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.04,0:25:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我若能去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.76,0:25:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是再高兴不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.90,0:25:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.87,0:25:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的情况比你想象的复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.73,0:25:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被困在这儿还有别的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.23,0:25:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.79,0:25:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  事实正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.63,0:25:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟我到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.35,0:25:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等着我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.39,0:25:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.07,0:25:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我想呆在这儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.06,0:25:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.30,0:25:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说联调局是唯一的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.70,0:26:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意  前门有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.78,0:26:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天眼组织的车
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.18,0:26:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在偷偷往外转移什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.33,0:26:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时准备行动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.39,0:26:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即行动  行动  上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.13,0:26:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不许动  -不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.90,0:26:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在方向盘上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.26,0:26:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在我们能看见的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.21,0:26:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好  先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.94,0:26:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么能为你们效劳的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.38,0:27:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯入局了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.24,0:27:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.19,0:27:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可有很长一段车程
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.43,0:27:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他带走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.80,0:27:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}晚上八点  马里布  雪松街1309号见  走便道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.01,0:27:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}信息已发送
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.57,0:28:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么萨城警局只有等着了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.33,0:28:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想用职权压人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.07,0:28:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若有必要我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.53,0:28:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯文  回头我再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.91,0:28:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.24,0:28:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.78,0:29:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看日落
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.75,0:29:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本  有些话我想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.77,0:29:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很早以前就应该跟你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.71,0:29:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.06,0:29:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚点再谢也不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.22,0:29:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.86,0:29:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须现在就说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.75,0:29:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.36,0:30:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你对我意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.06,0:30:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.28,0:30:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.74,0:30:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点忘了  我有个惊喜给你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.28,0:30:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这等我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.86,0:30:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.63,0:30:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.94,0:31:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}马里布
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.24,0:31:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(191.4,268)}加利福尼亚  马里布  简的住宅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.12,0:34:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.69,0:34:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.91,0:34:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.07,0:34:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是加州调查局探员
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.42,0:34:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我要征用你的车
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.72,0:34:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.78,0:34:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.62,0:35:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即下车  快
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.74,0:35:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.39,0:35:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.10,0:35:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要报警
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.47,0:35:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.17,0:35:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-简  -喂  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.23,0:35:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  别这么做  别扔下我这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.82,0:35:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.19,0:35:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  求你了  你身处险境
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.86,0:35:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.99,0:35:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.77,0:35:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.70,0:35:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样做是在自寻死路
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.86,0:35:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.80,0:35:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.15,0:35:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.28,0:37:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.26,0:37:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来早了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.65,0:37:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不早  来得正好  坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.72,0:37:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,911  您遇到了什么紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.63,0:37:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是加州调查局的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.00,0:37:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾莎·里斯本探员
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.80,0:37:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请派警员到马里布的雪松街1309号
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.84,0:37:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有探员需要立即支援
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.53,0:37:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你们五个聚在一起是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.66,0:37:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人可能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.98,0:37:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人可能猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.99,0:37:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们中的一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.38,0:37:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.07,0:38:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  在我们几个中间
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.68,0:38:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们其中之一是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.66,0:38:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.13,0:38:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是谁  -我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.19,0:38:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到这来就是为了找出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.38,0:38:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想说这个房间里的某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.50,0:38:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个连环杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.67,0:38:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我很确定  -太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.07,0:38:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证完全不荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.27,0:38:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证  我才不跟你在这儿胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.54,0:38:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.36,0:38:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步都别想往门口走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.85,0:38:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不准走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.73,0:38:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放轻松  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.36,0:38:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看起来很紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.68,0:38:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.49,0:38:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.08,0:38:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢把你们的枪拿出来  放在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.19,0:38:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推到我这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.29,0:39:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.82,0:39:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.22,0:39:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.43,0:39:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.82,0:39:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.65,0:39:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这才刚刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.63,0:39:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这一刻  我等了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.91,0:39:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多年来  血腥约翰一直很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.76,0:39:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们中的某个人一直很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.97,0:39:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很谨慎  除了这次
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.68,0:39:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一次  你露出马脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.83,0:39:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基拉·汀斯利死之前跟我说了件事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.77,0:39:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她告诉我杀她的人  也就是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.21,0:39:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.13,0:39:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三个点
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.82,0:39:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在肩膀上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.88,0:39:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都得
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:39:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.59,0:39:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻动手
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.10,0:40:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始脱吧  快
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.97,0:40:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.33,0:40:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.95,0:40:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.00,0:40:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想得那样
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.40,0:40:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你弄错了  -住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.58,0:40:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.82,0:40:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  等等  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.94,0:40:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.51,0:40:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.65,0:41:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.32,0:41:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到他们俩那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.21,0:41:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别动
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.34,0:41:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你们三个
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.51,0:41:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到墙边站着  快
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.31,0:41:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.69,0:41:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}马里布
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.62,0:42:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
